As a fan of Maze, it was quite disappointing to view this. The quality of the video was not good. It was not clear and appeared murky. It also appeared that Mr. Beverly had a cold. He was not as enthusiastic from previous performances that I've seen. The best live in concert DVD by Maze, by far, is Live in Los Angeles!!!!
